OL,4,CHomeowners to get 15 years to sue for
OL,5,C'shoddy' workmanship - minister
OL,6, Homeowners in England and Wales will
OL,7, get 15 years to legally challenge
OL,8, shoddy building work in light of the
OL,9, cladding crisis, a minister has said.
OL,11,FThis would increase the current
OL,12,Fsix-year period in which legal action
OL,13,Fcan be brought against developers.
OL,15,FHousing Secretary Robert Jenrick said
OL,16,Fthe change would "put new cards in the
OL,17,Fhands of the leaseholders".
OL,19,FHowever, speaking to the BBC one
OL,20,Fleaseholder described the announcement
OL,21,Fas "smoke and mirrors".
